  "texts": [
    "The training set consists of 10178 samples, and the test set has 1273 questions.MedQA was compiled with a choice of four (MedQA-4-option) or five possible answers, so we finetuned the models on the original 5-option dataset and tested it on both the 5-and 4-option questions to have comparable results with existing evaluations of medical LLMs.",
    "To finetune models for chain-of-thought reasoning, we used a training set in the distribution of MedQA that provides human-written explanations.",
    "MedMCQA:The MedMCQA [37] dataset consists of more than 194k multiple-choice questions with 4answer options from the Indian medical entrance examinations (AIIMS/NEET).",
    "This dataset covers 2.4k healthcare topics and 21 medical subjects.",
    "The training set contains 187k samples, and the validation set has 4183 questions."
